89	                    <dt>전체 / 성공 / 실패</dt>
90	                    <dd>
91	                        {summary.history.totalCount} / {summary.history.successCount} / {summary.history.failCount}
92	                    </dd>
93	                    <dt>중복 / staging</dt>
